    "body": "## Summary\nFix grammar errors where \"is not support\" should be \"is not supported\" or \"does not support\":\n\n- `vllm/attention/ops/merge_attn_states.py`: \"is not support for FP8\" → \"does not support FP8\"\n- `tests/quantization/test_compressed_tensors.py`: \"is not support on ROCm\" → \"is not supported on ROCm\" (3 occurrences)\n\n## Test plan\n- No functional changes, only grammar corrections in comments and skip messages\n- Verified files parse correctly with Python syntax check\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)",
